snippet.title: El Minero. Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
New indie 2D platformer for Windows, MacOS and Linux. 
Featuring Music from  Palmasur (Lo-Fi Mex) and ghostpops,

On sale! 
https://sketchyceviche.itch.io/el-minero 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2054330/El_Minero/
Demo available on itch.io.
